-- Government Officials Suspended Over 169 Coal-Mining Deaths, Daily Says
-- Ben Richardson
-- 2010-07-03T00:56:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-03/governmen-officials-suspended-over-169-coal-mining-deaths-daily-says.html

          
          
             Three city mayors were suspended
after 169 people were killed in accidents at coal mines that had
already been ordered to shut, China Daily said.  
          
          


  


        